Update: the more i play the more upset I get playing this. Tanks, trucks all got faster than my jet! Once the laser gun is pushed, the jet slow down to the point it is impossible not to get hit by tanks bullets or missiles. This whole game could have been very fun if only the developer corrects it from time to time. So far, I don't think it has any updates! For the longest time. Tough shooting down Mig is fun, I'm more disappointed with the 'Pay' version more than I thought. Control is difficult. And I hate it when they handicapped the laser power so badly it takes so many shots just to penetrate tanks and buildings. And without the powerful nuclear bomb like the free version, I jus couldn't get all those enemy missiles that come at me at the same time on higher levels. I like a good game. But i don't like an unfair, handicapped game just because the developer didn't have enough imagination.
